---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="行业洞察 - AI 技术博客" description="集信智能行业洞察栏目，分享 AI 技术趋势、企业智能化实践案例与行业深度分析。">
  <Header />
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">行业洞察</span>
      <h1>AI 行业前沿观察</h1>
      <p>探索人工智能技术趋势与企业智能化最佳实践</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-list">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="blog-grid">
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">🤖</div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <span class="blog-tag">技术前沿</span>
            <h2>大语言模型在企业场景中的落地实践</h2>
            <p>深入探讨如何将 LLM 技术有效整合到企业业务流程中，实现真正的业务价值。</p>
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span>2025-06-15</span>
              <a href="/blog/llm-enterprise-practice" class="read-more">阅读全文 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">💡</div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <span class="blog-tag">行业分析</span>
            <h2>2025 年企业 AI 趋势报告</h2>
            <p>从智能客服到流程自动化，盘点 2025 年最值得关注的企业 AI 应用趋势。</p>
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span>2025-05-20</span>
              <a href="/blog/ai-trends-2025" class="read-more">阅读全文 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-image">🔒</div>
          <div class="blog-content">
            <span class="blog-tag">最佳实践</span>
            <h2>企业 AI 数据安全与隐私保护指南</h2>
            <p>分析企业部署 AI 系统时需要关注的数据安全风险与合规要求。</p>
            <div class="blog-meta">
              <span>2025-04-10</span>
              <a href="/blog/ai-data-security" class="read-more">阅读全文 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #e0f2fe);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero h1 { font-size: 2.75rem; font-weight: 800; margin: 1rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .page-hero p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .blog-list { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .blog-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(360px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; }
  .blog-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .blog-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .blog-image {
    height: 200px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #e0f2fe);
  }
  .blog-content { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .blog-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .blog-content h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; line-height: 1.4; }
  .blog-content p { color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .blog-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  .read-more { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
